00:54:19.670 --> 00:54:20.270
PROFESSOR: That's true.

00:54:20.270 --> 00:54:21.520
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]

00:54:23.630 --> 00:54:27.670
PROFESSOR: Yeah so computers and
programming and computer

00:54:27.670 --> 00:54:29.370
science was offered
